  <brief_title>Study of TRM-1 (TRAIL-R1 Monoclonal Antibody) in Subjects With Relapsed or Refractory Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma (NHL)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Open-Label, Dose-Escalation Study to Evaluate the Safety, Efficacy, and Exposure to TRM-1 (Fully Human Monoclonal Antibody to the TRAIL-R1) in Subjects With Relapsed or Refractory Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
