  </sponsors>
  <source>Human Genome Sciences Inc.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, efficacy and exposure to TRM-1 in
      subjects with relapsed or refractory Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma (NHL).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
